name: Special House #2 - Fokusu House
description: It's a pixel sprite 120x120 upscale to 1200x1200 of Fokusu House. Fokusu (フォクス) mean fox in Japan, instead of using kitsune (狐, キツネ), i choose the katakana one. The reason why i create fox house, because kitsune/fox are believed to possess superior intelligence, long life, and magical powers.
